<item>
            <title>[OAK-396] Limit property index to nodes of given type</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OAK-396</link>
                <project id="12313221" key="OAK">Jackrabbit Oak</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;As discussed on the mailing list &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; the property index must be enhanced to take the node type into account.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;http://jackrabbit.markmail.org/thread/loudobqviwvhsli5&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://jackrabbit.markmail.org/thread/loudobqviwvhsli5&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
